            {
                "comment": "Dr. Gomez is a great person, he is very accommodating and gives a reasonable amount of time to complete assignments. He is very highly educated and knowledgeable about his course material. If you participate, do the readings and comprehend the material, this class should be relatively enjoyable. He is a great prof!",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "231 was a very participation heavy course. Show up, do the readings, and youll get an A. The major points were attendance, timed mini essays which were just 1 question from the provided guide (can be done easily if you read), and essays that are take home and you get a long time to work on them.",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "One of my favorite classes taught by one of my favorite professors. The course material was extremely interesting, and he's a wonderful professor. Do all of the readings and utilize the reading guides (which are helpful for the quizzes). Not a tough grader, and always willing to meet for office hours. I highly recommend taking a class with him.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 5
